.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, blues, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, tennis, basketball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the fan of indie is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
4. the fan of country is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the fan of blues is between the fan of ambient and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | country     | blues           | ambient | indie  |
| Sport         | soccer | basketball | swimming   | tennis |

