.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, disco, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the fan of metal is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the fan of classical is between the person driving the boat and the fan of disco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | metal | classical | disco      |
| Transport     | helicopter | boat    | scooter  | quad-bike |

