.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, cycling, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, bus, quad-bike
1. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person driving the bus##2
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | cricket | water-polo | cycling     | rowing   |
| Transport   | bus   | airplane     | quad-bike | van |

