.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, engineer, paramedic, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, roller, snowmobile
1. the paramedic is between the person driving the bus and the scientist##2
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the scientist##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | engineer | paramedic | scientist | electrician |
| Transport   | bus         | snowmobile       | skateboard    | roller         |

