.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, raspberry, peas, grapes
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, handball, cycling
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person eating raspberry and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | grapes   | peas      | raspberry   | carrot  |
| Sport   | cycling | skiing | handball | parkour |

