.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, artichoke, pumpkin, cabbage
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, zombie, martial-arts, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person eating artichoke is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating spinach##2
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | spinach     | artichoke | cabbage   | pumpkin        |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts   | zombie | western |

