.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, puzzles, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, salsa, classical, jazz
1. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the fan of salsa is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | puzzles | card-games | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | classical          | salsa     | jazz  | disco     |

