.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, french, polish, british
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, hedgehog, frog
1. the russian is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the british is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the ferret and the french##2
4. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | british | french | russian | polish |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | frog  | rat | ferret      |

