.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, filmmaking, gardening
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the van##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | gardening | reading | filmmaking | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | van    | snowmobile  | quad-bike    | boat       |

