The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, skiing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the dutch is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the french and the mexican##2
5. the mexican is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | dutch   | french   | argentine | mexican |
| Sport         | parkour | skateboarding | cycling     | skiing    |

