.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, magic-tricks, hiking
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, fish, rabbit
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | hiking     | gardening | drawing |
| Pet     | ferret | rabbit | fish       | goldfish     |

 